        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

        5.0 out of 5 stars Simple black toner cartridge replacement
        Reviewed in the United States on May 25, 2015
        Color: BlackVerified Purchase
        The LaserJet Toner cartridge carton arrived well packaged to protect the product and its enveloping carton. The instructions for replacing the cartridge were clear and straight-forward. The preparations including removing the cartridge from the bag that was inside the carton, then removing the bright orange toner dispenser cover, and extracting/pulling out the bright orange shipping tab. The actual cartridge replacement was as simple as lifting the printer lid, taking out the empty toner cartridge and replacing it with the new one, then closing the printer lid. The printer immediately detected the new cartridge and began its "new cartridge" cycling to prepare the new cartridge for its first print job. There was no spillage of the toner during this entire operation. Bottom-line, everything worked exactly as expected.
